<br>
*Steals a glance at Ankhami and notes her expectant glare before speaking*<br>
<br>
By orders of my Mistress Ankhami, I seek entrance into the Harvesters of Darkness. As some of you know, my great grandfather is responsible for a debt of blood owed to the lady, seeing as though my father and grandfather are both dead, that debt falls to me. I have given my word that I will serve her until she deems fit that the debt is paid.<br>
<br>
Part of me.... penance... is to join with you and offer my blades to you all. For this action I have been thrown out of my home, stripped of my rankings within the steel warriors and forced to join the dismal rage in the serwers of freeport.<br>
<br>
*glances up at his mistress again, biting hard upon his tongue before swallowing and giving a brief nod.*<br>
<br>
If there are any questions.... I would be... *bites out the word* honored.... to answer them.<br>
<br>
((ooc: Hello =) Just a little ooc back history here. Servantious is a shadow knight in the service of innoruuk, but as you can tell, he is a reluctant one at best. He's bound by the old chivalry ways of honor, he gives his word, he wont break it. He offers his sword, even if he doesnt want to, he will stand by that offer until he is dead or is no longer wanted.<br>
<br>
Ankhami and I have been working this story out for a good two or three weeks now and so far it's been alot of fun.)) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bharvestersofdarkness.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ankhami>Ankhami</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Yath'tallar of Vengance<br>
